Package: fenrir
Type: Package
Title: Scalable Inference for Bayesian Multinomial Logistic-Normal Dynamic Linear Models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-09-25
Authors@R: c(person("Manan", "Saxena", role=c("aut","cre"), 
                     email = "manansaxena05@gmail.com"),
            person("Justin", "Silverman", role=c("ctb"),
                     email = "Justin.Silverman@psu.edu"))
Maintainer: Manan Saxena <manansaxena05@gmail.com>
Description: Provides methods for scalable inference of Bayesian Multinomial Logistic-Normal Dynamic Linear Models using efficient MAP estimation 
             and Multinomial Dirichlet Bootstrap for uncertaninity qunatification. Implemented in C++ for scalability with an Rcpp wrapper for use in R.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 4.2.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp (>= 1.0.10), RcppEigen, RcppDist, RcppNumerical
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
